  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        All patients who come to the UC San Diego Surgical Specialties clinic and have chosen to
        undergo a ventral hernia repair will be evaluated for participation in this tria
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion:

          1. Umbilical or incisional hernia greater than 2 cm in size

          2. Female, age 18-75

          3. Mentally competent to give informed consent

          4. Scheduled to undergo a transvaginal NOTES ventral hernia repair

        Exclusion:

          1. Pregnant women

          2. Patients with defects measuring greater than 10 cm in size

          3. Patients with complex hernias requiring fascial mobilization for closure

          4. Morbidly obese patients (BMI &gt;45)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
